Your bot needs an identity:
Sign in to Microsoft's Application Registration Portal
Click Add an app 
If you see two app groupings, click the button in the Converged Applications section.
Choose a name for your bot (e.g. IVR Skype Bot) and click Create.
Copy the Application Id into the form on this page.
Click Generate New Password under Application Secrets.
Copy the Generated Password into the form on this page.
Complete the registration by clicking Save at the bottom of the page.
